'alevel-edx-bio-meiosis-variation': `<svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><style>@keyframes mv_cross{0%{transform:rotate(0deg)}100%{transform:rotate(360deg)}}@keyframes mv_fade{0%,100%{opacity:.3}50%{opacity:1}}.mv_c{animation:mv_fade 2s ease-in-out infinite}.mv_c2{animation:mv_fade 2s ease-in-out infinite .5s}.mv_c3{animation:mv_fade 2s ease-in-out infinite 1s}.mv_c4{animation:mv_fade 2s ease-in-out infinite 1.5s}</style></defs><text x="200" y="22" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" fill="var(--text)" font-family="sans-serif">Meiosis &amp; Variation</text><rect x="15" y="45" width="55" height="68" rx="5" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="mv_c"/><text x="42" y="62" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text)" font-family="sans-serif">Meiosis I</text><text x="42" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Homologs</text><text x="42" y="88" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">separate</text><text x="42" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">2n → n</text><rect x="78" y="45" width="55" height="68" rx="5" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="mv_c2"/><text x="105" y="62" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text)" font-family="sans-serif">Meiosis II</text><text x="105" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Chromatids</text><text x="105" y="88" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">separate</text><text x="105" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="6.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">4 cells</text><rect x="20" y="130" width="110" height="80" rx="6" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--border)" stroke-width="1"/><text x="75" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" font-weight="bold" fill="var(--text)" font-family="sans-serif">Crossing Over</text><text x="75" y="166" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Prophase I</text><text x="75" y="180" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Chiasma formed</text><text x="75" y="194" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">New allele combos</text><rect x="145" y="45" width="230" height="165" rx="6" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="var(--border)" stroke-width="1"/><text x="260" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" font-weight="bold" fill="var(--text)" font-family="sans-serif">Sources of Genetic Variation</text><text x="260" y="88" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">1. Crossing over (chiasma)</text><text x="260" y="106" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">2. Independent assortment</text><text x="260" y="124" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">3. Random fertilisation</text><text x="260" y="142" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">4. Mutation (point/frame)</text><text x="260" y="160" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Continuous vs discontinuous</text><text x="260" y="178" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">variation · Normal distribution</text><text x="200" y="250" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Diploid (2n) → 4 haploid (n) gametes · Sexual reproduction</text><text x="200" y="267" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="sans-serif">Polyploidy · Karyotype · Non-disjunction (Down syndrome)</text></svg>`,

